\section{Summary}
\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Summary}

 

\begin{itemize}
 
 \item Previous work:


 \begin{itemize}
\item Eergy bands are non-parabolic even very close to the $\Gamma$-point, and the effective masses are \textbf{k}-dependency.
\item  The dielectric function calculated by our theoretical method shows a good agreement with the result of experiment.
\end{itemize}




